    <item>
      <title>在巴拿马困境中，第一量子停止派息并出售矿山</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/first-quantum-to-cut-spending-sell-mines-after-panama-setback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第一量子矿业有限公司 (First Quantum Minerals Ltd.) 在被勒令关闭其在巴拿马价值 100 亿美元的铜矿业务后，将削减支出、暂停派息并出售小型矿山，以全面释放现金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/first-quantum-to-cut-spending-sell-mines-after-panama-setback</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 22:13:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
